nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.maze.actors

Interface Actor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Bug, Chap, Enemy

    public interface Actor
    An Actor that can move around on the board and interact with items an tiles. In order to be able to make instances of implementations of this implementations must have either a zero argument constructor or a public static build(ActorInfo) method.
